{
  "id": "RAW_f9667060",
  "title": "88%的公司在用 AI，但只有 39%吃到真金白银？麦肯锡 2025 AI 报告来了",
  "url": "https://www.qbitai.com/2025/11/350538.html",
  "date": "2025-11-10 08:08:18",
  "author": "梦瑶",
  "siteName": "量子位",
  "content": "<!--摘要样式-->\n<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <blockquote style=\"border:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 16px;margin:0px !important 0px 20px 0px;background-size:initial;color:#707070;background-attachment:initial;font-size:18px;line-height:1.64;background-position:initial;quotes:none;background-repeat:initial;background-clip:initial;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;background-image:initial;background-origin:initial;text-align:justify;\">\n   <p class=\"pgc-h-forward-slash\" style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px !important;\" data-track=\"91\">梦瑶 发自 凹非寺</p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-h-forward-slash\" style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px !important;\" data-track=\"92\">量子位 | 公众号 QbitAI</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"2\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">麦肯锡</span>刚刚发布了<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">2025年AI最新报告</span>，一组数据让人“破防”：</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"3\">88%的组织都在用AI，但只有39%的组织吃出了“真金白银”。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"4\">这份<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">《The state of AI in 2025》</span>回答了AI时代大家都很关心的一个问题：</p>\n  <blockquote style=\"border:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 16px;margin:20px 0px;background-size:initial;color:#707070;background-attachment:initial;font-size:18px;line-height:1.64;background-position:initial;quotes:none;background-repeat:initial;background-clip:initial;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;background-image:initial;background-origin:initial;text-align:justify;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75;\" data-track=\"5\">用了AI之后，大家到底过得怎么样？</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:18px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\">\n   <p><img alt=\"88%的公司在用AI，但只有39%吃到真金白银？麦肯锡2025 AI报告来了\" class=\"syl-page-img\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: block; border-radius: 4px;\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251110120955_a723897a9a02f533990faa2cbcefb274.png\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251110120955_a723897a9a02f533990faa2cbcefb274.png\"></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 20px 0px 0px !important 0px;\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"6\">总共有5个结论：</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"7\">1.多数企业已在至少一个业务环节使用AI，AI几乎已成标配。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"8\">2.看似大家都在用AI，但真能用到“见效赚钱”的，其实不到四成。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"9\">3.人人都在谈Agent，但真正跑通业务流程的企业，仍是少数派。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"10\">4.只有高绩效企业能真正尝到AI红利。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"11\">5.AI岗位正吃掉招聘预算，传统岗位被替代、AI人才被争夺，组织结构正在被重写。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"13\">麦肯锡这份《The State of AI in 2025》调查了全球来自各行业的近2000家组织，其中一个最直观的数字是：</p>\n  <blockquote style=\"border:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 16px;margin:20px 0px;background-size:initial;color:#707070;background-attachment:initial;font-size:18px;line-height:1.64;background-position:initial;quotes:none;background-repeat:initial;background-clip:initial;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;background-image:initial;background-origin:initial;text-align:justify;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75;\" data-track=\"14\">88%的受访企业表示已在至少一个业务职能中使用AI技术，比去年整整高出了10个百分点。</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"15\">但，用上不等于用深，更不等于用出钱。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"16\">看着很热闹，真正能赚到钱的却不多，不少企业想靠Agent一步起飞，但更多的还停在起跑线观望。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"18\">单从数据看，AI确实在企业里全面开花，大多数企业已经不再是观望者，而是参与者（哪怕只是试水）：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:18px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\">\n   <p><img alt=\"88%的公司在用AI，但只有39%吃到真金白银？麦肯锡2025 AI报告来了\" class=\"syl-page-img\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: block; border-radius: 4px;\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251110120955_729be2f248effe5de35dc84e007d99da.png\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251110120955_729be2f248effe5de35dc84e007d99da.png\"></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 20px 0px 0px !important 0px;\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"19\">但试水不代表游泳，更不代表能游到终点。</p>\n  <blockquote style=\"border:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 16px;margin:20px 0px;background-size:initial;color:#707070;background-attachment:initial;font-size:18px;line-height:1.64;background-position:initial;quotes:none;background-repeat:initial;background-clip:initial;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;background-image:initial;background-origin:initial;text-align:justify;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75;\" data-track=\"20\">报告显示，只有39%的组织表示AI带来了实质性财务回报，实现了息税前利润（EBIT）的增长。</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"21\">也就是说，多数企业AI项目还没有跑赢投入产出比：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:18px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\">\n   <p><img class=\"syl-page-img\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: block; border-radius: 4px;\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251110120955_73a0c052cb742f3c61196822b3f2cf47.png\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251110120955_73a0c052cb742f3c61196822b3f2cf47.png\"></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 20px 0px 0px !important 0px;\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"22\">这39%，基本来自少数行业场景的集中收割。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"23\">例如软件工程、制造、IT这类以<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">效率提效</span>为核心的岗位更容易吃到红利，而营销、战略、财务则是为数不多能带来“营收提升”的领域：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:18px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\">\n   <p><img class=\"syl-page-img\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: block; border-radius: 4px;\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251110120955_41ea3e41dc5b22b38519c407f1e78ae3.png\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251110120955_41ea3e41dc5b22b38519c407f1e78ae3.png\"></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 20px 0px 0px !important 0px;\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"24\">也正因如此，很多企业的AI使用呈现出一种<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">效率提升 ≠ 盈利提升</span>的割裂状态：</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"25\">流程顺了，但财务账面并没太大变化。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"27\">生成式AI余温未散，Agent就已成为企业新宠。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"28\">报告显示，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">62%</span>的受访组织已经在试验AI Agent类应用，不少还搭建了自己的<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">企业内部Agent</span>，例如AI客服助手、AI知识总结助手、AI代码生成工具等。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"29\">更关键的是：在任何一个部门里，真正在推AI Agent的公司，都不到一成。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"30\">而这些真正“跑起来”的应用，也主要集中在流程清晰、标准化程度高的部门，例如 IT运维、知识管理、营销与销售等：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:18px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\">\n   <p><img class=\"syl-page-img\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: block; border-radius: 4px;\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251110120955_67f640d2bbef42edd8686399fc7cce0f.png\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251110120955_67f640d2bbef42edd8686399fc7cce0f.png\"></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 20px 0px 0px !important 0px;\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"31\">进一步拆解后会发现，这些使用Agent的场景有一个共同点：结构清晰、流程标准、数据充分、容错率高。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"32\">而一旦涉及跨部门协作、复杂流程或高风险决策，Agent往往就会止步于试验阶段。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"33\">根源也不难理解。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"34\">麦肯锡在报告中明确指出：部署Agent不是接个API就完事了，而是要<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">重构流程+重塑组织+重训员工</span>。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"35\">也正因如此，麦肯锡在报告中反复强调，Agent热度虽高，但还<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">远未量产</span>。多数组织目前还在试用或“验证阶段，离<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">规模化</span>还有一段距离。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"37\">如果说AI是企业的新晋员工，那它目前的表现大概是，工作流程顺了不少，但月底账上钱还是没多出几位数。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"38\">首先，麦肯锡报告里提到，64%的受访组织都表示自从用了AI以后感觉更有创新力了：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:18px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\">\n   <p><img class=\"syl-page-img\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: block; border-radius: 4px;\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251110120956_fce23945ca9f9e286cec5149ec3e5ce9.png\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251110120956_fce23945ca9f9e286cec5149ec3e5ce9.png\"></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 20px 0px 0px !important 0px;\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"39\">也就是说，AI确实给了大家带来了一种变强了的实感。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"40\">团队做事更快了、响应更灵了、开会更少了、脑子更清楚了～</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"41\">但这份好感度尚未大面积转化为<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">收入增长——</span></p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"42\">仅<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">36%</span>的企业表示盈利能力有所提高，仅<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">33%</span>看到收入增长，而报告中最冷的一项——市场份额提升，仅有<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">25%</span>的企业认为得到了改善。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"43\">那么现在AI到底帮企业干了什么？</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"44\">从岗位来看，它现在还是在后端环节更能显出“立竿见影”的降本效果：</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"45\">有40%的组织用AI做知识管理，有34%的组织把AI派去管IT，有26%的组织把应用在软件工程。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"46\">而真正“能上分”的业务前线主要集中在三大类：</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"47\">39%的营销销售部门用AI写文案、做内容、找线索，精准获客提转化；31%的产品开发团队依赖AI做版本快速迭代、辅助测试；17%的战略与财务规划部门则利用AI做预测建模、算ROI、做预算分析：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:18px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\">\n   <p><img class=\"syl-page-img\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: block; border-radius: 4px;\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251110120955_2ab76360a835aa1b49967b1ad61f53cd.png\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251110120955_2ab76360a835aa1b49967b1ad61f53cd.png\"></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 20px 0px 0px !important 0px;\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"49\">不是谁用AI，谁就能吃到红利。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"50\">在这波AI浪潮中，普通企业还在“用一用、试试看”，而高绩效企业早已杀进了业务流程，把AI用出了真章。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"52\">麦肯锡这次报告中，把一类企业单独拉了出来看：</p>\n  <blockquote style=\"border:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 16px;margin:20px 0px;background-size:initial;color:#707070;background-attachment:initial;font-size:18px;line-height:1.64;background-position:initial;quotes:none;background-repeat:initial;background-clip:initial;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;background-image:initial;background-origin:initial;text-align:justify;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75;\" data-track=\"53\">那些能将至少5%的企业EBIT（息税前利润）增长归因于AI，并已在实际业务中实现显著价值回报的组织，被定义为AI高绩效企业。</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"54\">麦肯锡这次把这类企业和拉出来比了一下，结果发现了一个惊人的差异：</p>\n  <blockquote style=\"border:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 16px;margin:20px 0px;background-size:initial;color:#707070;background-attachment:initial;font-size:18px;line-height:1.64;background-position:initial;quotes:none;background-repeat:initial;background-clip:initial;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;background-image:initial;background-origin:initial;text-align:justify;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75;\" data-track=\"55\">未来3年，有50%的高绩效企业打算推动AI主导的“变革性改变”，而普通企业中这一比例只有14%。</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:18px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\">\n   <p><img class=\"syl-page-img\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: block; border-radius: 4px;\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251110120955_e2d9ba501357c325b90996a388fdadfb.png\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251110120955_e2d9ba501357c325b90996a388fdadfb.png\"></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 20px 0px 0px !important 0px;\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"56\">更重要的是，这种“变革性改变”不是空口号，而是正在发生的事。</p>\n  <blockquote style=\"border:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 16px;margin:20px 0px;background-size:initial;color:#707070;background-attachment:initial;font-size:18px;line-height:1.64;background-position:initial;quotes:none;background-repeat:initial;background-clip:initial;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;background-image:initial;background-origin:initial;text-align:justify;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75;\" data-track=\"57\">在AI真正落地的环节上，高绩效员工从从根本上重新设计工作流程的可能性高达55%，约其他人的三倍（2.8×）。</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:18px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\">\n   <p><img class=\"syl-page-img\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: block; border-radius: 4px;\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251110120955_ff688878aafaa83e378a291ce0ed57ea.png\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251110120955_ff688878aafaa83e378a291ce0ed57ea.png\"></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 20px 0px 0px !important 0px;\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"58\">相比之下，那些还停留在省点人工、做点报表的企业，可能根本没触碰到AI的真正红利区。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"59\">麦肯锡合作方专家Tara Balakrishnan也在报告中指出，高绩效企业/人才最突出的特征是野心的高度，他们的AI战略并不止步于效率提升，而是试图重塑整个业务模式。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"60\">在他看来，成本导向思维正在限制AI的潜力，真正能够规模化使用AI、并持续获得生产力提升的企业，往往也正是那些把AI当作增长与创新引擎、拥有清晰变革叙事的团队。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"61\">当然了，高绩效AI组织的成功也并非偶然。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"62\">麦肯锡从战略、技术、人才、数据、运营五大维度梳理出近20项AI最佳实践，结果发现一个显著差异：</p>\n  <blockquote style=\"border:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 16px;margin:20px 0px;background-size:initial;color:#707070;background-attachment:initial;font-size:18px;line-height:1.64;background-position:initial;quotes:none;background-repeat:initial;background-clip:initial;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;background-image:initial;background-origin:initial;text-align:justify;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75;\" data-track=\"63\">AI绩效越高的企业，几乎在每一项实践上都做得更早、更深入。</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"64\">比如，在战略层面，高绩效企业中有60%已绘制明确的AI路线图（一般企业的一半）。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"65\">在组织执行层面，它们不止停留在“用AI试试”的阶段，而是主动重写业务流程，将AI嵌入前线流程与系统，采用敏捷开发模式，追求“快速试错-持续迭代”的落地节奏。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:18px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\">\n   <p><img class=\"syl-page-img\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: block; border-radius: 4px;\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251110120955_bec78f97d03bfde6e6590fd8d7739f94.png\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251110120955_bec78f97d03bfde6e6590fd8d7739f94.png\"></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 20px 0px 0px !important 0px;\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"66\">AI红利并不平均，它更像一场结构性机会，属于那些愿意打破流程重做一遍的人。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"68\">AI正在改写的不止是企业的业务流程，还有员工的生存逻辑。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"69\">麦肯锡报告显示，未来一年内，32%的受访企业预计员工总数将下降，仅13%预计会上升，多数则认为“总体变化不大”。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:18px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\">\n   <p><img class=\"syl-page-img\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: block; border-radius: 4px;\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251110120955_479bc00d24ad4be2db802f338eb52815.png\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251110120955_479bc00d24ad4be2db802f338eb52815.png\"></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 20px 0px 0px !important 0px;\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"70\">看似平稳的数据背后，是组织架构的悄然重构：“裁得动的被裁了，裁不动的正在学习AI技能。”</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"71\">被替代的，是重复性强、创造力低的岗位；而被紧急招聘的，是那些能驾驭AI、驱动新能力的关键角色：</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"72\">软件工程师、数据工程师、AI产品经理、Prompt Engineer、AI伦理与合规专家……这些原本“偏技术”的岗位，正从边角料变成招聘主角。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"73\">与此同时，企业之间的AI人才分化也越拉越大。</p>\n  <blockquote style=\"border:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 16px;margin:20px 0px;background-size:initial;color:#707070;background-attachment:initial;font-size:18px;line-height:1.64;background-position:initial;quotes:none;background-repeat:initial;background-clip:initial;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;background-image:initial;background-origin:initial;text-align:justify;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75;\" data-track=\"74\">大企业在AI相关岗位的招聘比例，是中小企业的两倍。</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"75\">有资源、有预判的大公司正在加速囤人，而人力紧张的小组织，则被迫经历一段AI转型的空窗期。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:18px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\">\n   <p><img class=\"syl-page-img\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: block; border-radius: 4px;\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251110120955_af68a479fa4b12339564da783ca764a0.png\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251110120955_af68a479fa4b12339564da783ca764a0.png\"></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 20px 0px 0px !important 0px;\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"76\">人才结构的变化背后，其实对应着另一个关键词：风险承压能力。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"77\">麦肯锡的调研显示，在所有AI相关的负面后果中，“结果不准确”是企业遇到最多的问题，有30%的组织在过去一年中至少遇到过一次该类风险。其次是“解释性不足”和“个人隐私问题”。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"78\">不过，真正令人关注的是另一组数据：</p>\n  <blockquote style=\"border:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 16px;margin:20px 0px;background-size:initial;color:#707070;background-attachment:initial;font-size:18px;line-height:1.64;background-position:initial;quotes:none;background-repeat:initial;background-clip:initial;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;background-image:initial;background-origin:initial;text-align:justify;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75;\" data-track=\"79\">在所有AI风险治理行为中，最积极的仍然是那批<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">高绩效AI组织</span>。</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:18px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\">\n   <p><img class=\"syl-page-img\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: block; border-radius: 4px;\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251110120956_2e7e0561f441585641d2a1b6423caddb.jpeg\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251110120956_2e7e0561f441585641d2a1b6423caddb.jpeg\"></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 20px 0px 0px !important 0px;\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"80\">他们在“知识产权侵犯”“合规问题”等关键风险上，既是遭遇者，也是最早进行防御部署的群体。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"81\">这一点，麦肯锡全球高级合伙人Alexander Sukharevsky给出的解释非常到位：</p>\n  <blockquote style=\"border:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 16px;margin:20px 0px;background-size:initial;color:#707070;background-attachment:initial;font-size:18px;line-height:1.64;background-position:initial;quotes:none;background-repeat:initial;background-clip:initial;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;background-image:initial;background-origin:initial;text-align:justify;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75;\" data-track=\"82\">正因为他们用得更深，用得更激进，所以风险也来得更快、更集中。</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"83\">这并不是坏事。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"84\">这些“高绩效组织”通常部署了比其他企业多两倍的AI用例，意味着他们往往是在关键任务场景里使用AI。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"85\">比如涉及隐私的数据流、核心业务流程的优化、员工、客户交互的自动化等等,这些环节天然就要求“高风险承受力+高执行效率”。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"86\">这也给尚在探索阶段的企业一个提示：</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"87\">真正高绩效的组织，反而是那些目标明确、策略清晰，能在创新中解决问题的团队。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"88\">只有当AI被当作“业务变革引擎”而不是“省人工工具”，它才能带来可衡量的长期价值。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"89\">更多细节欢迎查看完整报告。</p>\n  <p style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;font-size:18px;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-track=\"90\">报告链接：\n   <br class=\"sysbr\" style=\"display: inline;\">\n   https://www.mckinsey.com/capabilities/quantumblack/our-insights/the-state-of-ai</p>\n  <!--版权声明-->\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "麦肯锡 2025 年 AI 报告揭示，88%的企业已采用 AI，但仅 39%实现显著财务回报，高绩效企业正通过重塑业务模式而非仅提升效率来获取 AI 红利。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "麦肯锡 2025 年 AI 报告揭示，88%的企业已采用 AI，但仅 39%实现显著财务回报，高绩效企业正通过重塑业务模式而非仅提升效率来获取 AI 红利。",
  "summary": "量子位发布的麦肯锡 2025 年 AI 报告《The state of AI in 2025》指出，尽管 88%的组织已在至少一个业务环节使用 AI，但仅 39%从中获得了息税前利润（EBIT）的增长，揭示了 AI 普及与实际商业回报之间的显著差距。报告核心结论包括：AI 已成为企业标配但效益转化不足；AI Agent 应用虽热门但落地率低，需重构流程与组织；AI 红利集中于高绩效企业，它们将 AI 视为增长而非成本工具；AI 正重塑组织结构和人才需求，引发岗位替代与人才争夺；高绩效企业在深度应用 AI 的同时也更积极地管理其风险。报告强调，AI 的真正价值在于驱动业务变革，而非仅提升效率，这要求企业在战略、技术、人才、数据和运营等多维度进行深入实践和持续迭代。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 普及与实际回报脱节：多数企业已采用 AI，但仅 39%实现了显著财务回报",
      "explanation": "报告指出 AI 已成企业标配，但多数 AI 项目尚未跑赢投入产出比，因应用停留在效率提升而非业务模式重塑，未能带来实质性盈利增长。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI Agent 应用尚处早期：真正跑通业务流程的企业不足一成，且需重构流程与组织",
      "explanation": "尽管 Agent 概念热门，但其部署不仅是技术接入，更需重构流程、重塑组织和重训员工，多数企业仍处于试验或验证阶段，离规模化应用尚远。"
    },
    {
      "point": "高绩效企业引领 AI 变革：将 AI 视为增长与创新引擎，通过重塑业务模式获取红利",
      "explanation": "仅少数高绩效企业能将 AI 深度融入核心业务，通过清晰的 AI 路线图和敏捷开发，实现变革性改变，而非满足于效率提升，从而获得结构性红利。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 重塑组织与人才结构：重复性岗位被替代，AI 相关技能岗位需求激增",
      "explanation": "AI 应用导致企业内部岗位结构变化，对软件工程师、AI 产品经理等新兴 AI 人才的需求显著上升，大企业加速囤积人才，引发人才分化。"
    },
    {
      "point": "高绩效企业更积极管理 AI 风险：因深度应用而更早遭遇风险，但也更早部署防御措施",
      "explanation": "这表明高风险承受力与高执行效率是高绩效组织的特征，它们将 AI 视为业务变革引擎，并在创新中解决风险问题，而非回避风险。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "88%的组织都在用 AI，但只有 39%的组织吃出了'真金白银'。",
    "麦肯锡在报告中明确指出：部署 Agent 不是接个 API 就完事了，而是要重构流程+重塑组织+重训员工。",
    "成本导向思维正在限制 AI 的潜力，真正能够规模化使用 AI、并持续获得生产力提升的企业，往往也正是那些把 AI 当作增长与创新引擎、拥有清晰变革叙事的团队。",
